          "type": "text",
          "style": "body",
          "content": "Students can file a complaint in writing via email addressed to the campus president at info@atldentalassistant.com. The president will review and respond to all complaints within 24 hours."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "style": "body",
          "content": "If a student is unhappy with the decision from the president, they have the right to submit the complaint through the GNPEC complaint portal at https://gnpec.georgia.gov/student-resources/complaints-against-institution."
        },
